title: Lakers, LeBron James, Antonio Brown, NBA top 10
itunes:title: Lakers, LeBron James, Antonio Brown, NBA top 10
description:
Colin discusses the latest rumors about F LeBron James and the Los Angeles Lakers, teams that want no part of Pittsburgh Steelers WR Antonio Brown, and the top 10 players in the NBA. Guests include Chris Broussard, Matt Barnes, and Vernon Davis.
